1
00:00:16,160 --> 00:00:18,360
[Huiyin Hall]

2
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,930
Your Highness, please take a rest.

3
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,760
You've been writing all day.

4
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:26,280
Hasn't Xiao Wuyi confessed yet?

5
00:00:26,710 --> 00:00:28,030
Forgive me, Your Highness.

6
00:00:28,030 --> 00:00:29,350
No matter how he's tortured,

7
00:00:29,350 --> 00:00:31,550
Xiao Wuyi remains silent.

8
00:00:31,830 --> 00:00:33,320
He only asked the jailers
for a brush and ink

9
00:00:33,320 --> 00:00:34,920
to finish his military book.

10
00:00:35,110 --> 00:00:36,520
Without Your Highness's permission,

11
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,670
the jailers didn't dare to give him those.

12
00:00:37,670 --> 00:00:41,000
So Xiao Wuyi dips his finger in blood
and continues to write.

13
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:44,240
What about the divorce paper?

14
00:00:44,240 --> 00:00:45,300
He didn't write it.

15
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,650
Then force him to write!

16
00:00:48,710 --> 00:00:51,100
Once it's written,
send it to Prince Jing'an's Mansion!

17
00:00:51,100 --> 00:00:52,820
Tell the Commandant of Justice that

18
00:00:52,820 --> 00:00:55,710
the evidence of Prince Jing'an's Household's
treason and corruption is conclusive.

19
00:00:55,710 --> 00:00:57,910
If he can't get Xiao Wuyi's confession,

20
00:00:57,930 --> 00:00:59,110
Xiao Ju's will do,

21
00:00:59,110 --> 00:01:00,200
or Xiao Yao's!

22
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,180
Grand Tutor was right.

23
00:01:05,150 --> 00:01:07,680
Prince Jing'an's Household
is too stubborn.

24
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:11,760
We might as well take this opportunity
and completely bring them down.

25
00:01:11,760 --> 00:01:12,400
Yes.

26
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:43,910
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

27
00:02:44,070 --> 00:02:46,880
[Episode 23]

28
00:03:06,530 --> 00:03:09,060
Xiao and his 2 sons embezzled canal funds,

29
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:10,490
illegally sold military supplies,

30
00:03:10,490 --> 00:03:11,820
and committed treason.

31
00:03:12,150 --> 00:03:13,680
Their mansion is now sealed off.

32
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,800
By the Regent's grace,

33
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,750
those who are not members
of the Xiao family may leave.

34
00:03:16,750 --> 00:03:19,400
Anyone who refuses will be sealed
inside the mansion immediately.

35
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,490
Except for the Dowager Princess,

36
00:03:20,490 --> 00:03:21,440
everyone else has left.

37
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:23,520
Master He is just a teacher
hired by our family.

38
00:03:23,520 --> 00:03:25,630
And Ruisheng is our physician.

39
00:03:25,950 --> 00:03:27,920
Aren't they a goddaughter and a concubine?

40
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:28,680
And what about the child?

41
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,970
Master He belongs to the He family

42
00:03:29,970 --> 00:03:31,360
and has nothing to do with the Xiaos.

43
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,430
As for Yu Ruisheng,

44
00:03:32,430 --> 00:03:34,420
she has never been
part of Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

45
00:03:34,420 --> 00:03:36,079
She is an official
of the Beifu Army Medical Office

46
00:03:36,079 --> 00:03:37,329
and receives her salary from Beifu.

47
00:03:37,329 --> 00:03:38,260
As for Duan Ziqi,

48
00:03:38,380 --> 00:03:39,990
he is certainly not Xiao Wuyi's son.

49
00:03:39,990 --> 00:03:41,120
And the Dowager Princess—

50
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,480
if I remember correctly,

51
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:45,170
according to the laws of Ye,
women over fifty awaiting trial

52
00:03:45,170 --> 00:03:46,500
can be confined at home.

53
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:47,640
Is that right?

54
00:03:48,390 --> 00:03:49,110
As for me...

55
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,829
What is that in your hand?

56
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:55,030
This is Young Lord Xiao's divorce paper.

57
00:03:55,030 --> 00:03:56,710
Your Highness, the Regent wants you

58
00:03:56,710 --> 00:03:58,570
to think carefully for yourself.

59
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,630
Please convey my word

60
00:04:04,850 --> 00:04:06,040
to Prince Qi.

61
00:04:06,730 --> 00:04:09,170
Tomorrow is the deadline.

62
00:04:11,780 --> 00:04:12,570
Report!

63
00:04:15,500 --> 00:04:16,570
Your Highness,

64
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:18,240
Liu Zhaolin,
an editor from Zhengtong Bookstore,

65
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:19,769
has come to turn himself in.

66
00:04:19,829 --> 00:04:21,560
Wasn't Liu Zhaolin already...

67
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:22,750
Report!

68
00:04:24,400 --> 00:04:26,400
Congratulations, Your Highness.

69
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:27,830
For what?

70
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:29,190
Your Highness,

71
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,920
the blood stasis in Xiao Wuyi's brain
has been there for nearly 3 years

72
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:33,720
and has become a chronic illness.

73
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,930
Rest assured, Your Highness.

74
00:04:34,930 --> 00:04:36,780
Once his meridians are completely blocked,

75
00:04:36,780 --> 00:04:37,950
he won't survive.

76
00:04:38,310 --> 00:04:39,400
In my humble opinion,

77
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:41,530
Xiao Wuyi will not live past this year.

78
00:04:42,960 --> 00:04:43,690
How dare you!

79
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:47,760
When did I ever say
I wanted Xiao Wuyi dead?

80
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:49,409
I'm telling you.

81
00:04:49,690 --> 00:04:51,350
If Xiao Wuyi doesn't recover,

82
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:54,000
I will bury the entire
Imperial Medical Bureau with him!

83
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:54,600
Get out!

84
00:04:56,010 --> 00:04:56,530
Yes.

85
00:05:01,700 --> 00:05:02,830
If we don't eliminate Northern Qin

86
00:05:02,830 --> 00:05:03,680
and reclaim our land,

87
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,390
there won't be true peace!

88
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,600
Yizhi.

89
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,920
This is what you told me yourself

90
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,450
while fleeing to Jiankang.

91
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,950
Have you forgotten?

92
00:05:16,230 --> 00:05:17,760
Don't be trapped in the past

93
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:20,130
and let it become your inner demon.

94
00:05:21,960 --> 00:05:23,690
You are not this kind of person.

95
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:25,800
Report!

96
00:05:26,890 --> 00:05:27,750
Your Highness,

97
00:05:28,720 --> 00:05:29,480
the jailers said that

98
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:31,040
before Young Lord Xiao fainted, he said

99
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,230
he had no crimes to confess,

100
00:05:32,230 --> 00:05:33,760
and that if he must confess,

101
00:05:34,220 --> 00:05:37,280
this military book written in blood
is his confession.

102
00:05:40,870 --> 00:05:41,870
Summon Xie Jiayu.

103
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:43,760
Yes.

104
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:45,680
No.

105
00:05:47,270 --> 00:05:47,950
Forget it.

106
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:51,480
Have Xie Jiayu go directly to the prison

107
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:52,740
and take Xiao Wuyi out.

108
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,490
Yes.

109
00:05:57,180 --> 00:06:00,500
[Court of Judicial Review]

110
00:06:38,510 --> 00:06:39,310
You dictate,

111
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:43,770
♪ What's the cost
of going against the wind? ♪

112
00:06:41,620 --> 00:06:42,880
and I'll write it down.

113
00:06:44,590 --> 00:06:48,280
♪ Knowing you, knowing me,
we live up to our promises ♪

114
00:06:48,300 --> 00:06:52,500
♪ Aligning the traces of our conviction ♪

115
00:06:52,620 --> 00:06:55,090
♪ As long as I'm with you ♪

116
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:55,110
Anyone who uses formations...

117
00:06:55,110 --> 00:06:58,090
♪ The journey can stretch on forever ♪

118
00:06:58,110 --> 00:07:01,870
♪ Even if it puts my life on the line ♪

119
00:07:01,890 --> 00:07:04,580
♪ I shall never forget ♪

120
00:07:04,670 --> 00:07:09,050
♪ Let me dash toward where you are ♪

121
00:07:09,080 --> 00:07:12,510
♪ To seek out my own sanctuary ♪

122
00:07:12,530 --> 00:07:15,320
♪ Life hurries by, yet you alone ♪

123
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:18,340
♪ Illuminate me
with your blazing radiance ♪

124
00:07:18,370 --> 00:07:22,420
♪ Let me burn with courage
as I forge ahead ♪

125
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:25,930
♪ Your hand in my hand ♪

126
00:07:25,950 --> 00:07:28,870
♪ Our love knows no bounds
of time or space ♪

127
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:34,430
♪ Two hearts together
until the end of time ♪

128
00:07:36,640 --> 00:07:37,350
Done.

129
00:07:40,320 --> 00:07:42,050
Can you go home with me now?

130
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,880
Pack these manuscripts up

131
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,960
and give them to Prince Qi
and the Department of State Affairs.

132
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,480
This is your life's work.

133
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,290
If you teach them,

134
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,090
aren't you afraid of being replaced?

135
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,680
Isn't that exactly what I want?

136
00:07:59,630 --> 00:08:00,830
Don't you want

137
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,630
there to be more Xiao Wuyis in Ye?

138
00:08:03,070 --> 00:08:05,400
Are you really making your final arrange—

139
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,850
Even if you want to die,

140
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,610
you have to hold on for a few more years.

141
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:18,750
Right now,

142
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:22,600
the world needs an invincible Xiao Wuyi.

143
00:08:24,410 --> 00:08:26,170
Let's go. Let's go home.

144
00:08:27,270 --> 00:08:28,070
Let's go home.

145
00:08:40,450 --> 00:08:41,020
Let's go.

146
00:08:56,290 --> 00:08:56,930
Wuyi!

147
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:00,080
Mother?

148
00:09:02,130 --> 00:09:02,840
Father?

149
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,450
Brother?

150
00:09:07,740 --> 00:09:08,390
You...

151
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,240
Let's go home.

152
00:09:15,550 --> 00:09:16,730
That's my son!

153
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:17,850
Be gentle!

154
00:09:18,370 --> 00:09:20,900
How can he stand you
patting him like that now?

155
00:09:24,880 --> 00:09:25,430
Let's go.

156
00:09:26,390 --> 00:09:27,030
Okay.

157
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:29,000
Let's go home.

158
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:32,730
[Shezhang Hall]

159
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,370
Why did you let Xiao Wuyi go?

160
00:09:36,810 --> 00:09:37,450
You...

161
00:09:40,400 --> 00:09:41,060
This was...

162
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,240
This was the only chance to bring
Prince Jing'an's Household down

163
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:46,510
and take back the command
of Beifu Army!

164
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:49,320
Don't you want to avenge

165
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,050
your mother?

166
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,850
If Xiao Ju hadn't concealed the truth,

167
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:56,550
how could the An and Lu families
have been wrongfully destroyed?

168
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:57,480
Xie Jiayu brought

169
00:09:57,480 --> 00:10:01,080
the letters between you and the wet nurse
of Prince Qi's Mansion,

170
00:10:01,120 --> 00:10:03,040
threatening to reveal my identity

171
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:04,500
to make me let Xiao Wuyi go.

172
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:07,010
Should I have let him go or not?

173
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:13,250
So she came to me specifically that day

174
00:10:14,010 --> 00:10:15,370
for this?

175
00:10:16,460 --> 00:10:19,360
Oh, right, Liu Zhaolin turned himself in.

176
00:10:24,840 --> 00:10:25,390
Him?

177
00:10:27,170 --> 00:10:28,630
He wouldn't dare say much.

178
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:32,330
Yes, he has committed suicide
out of fear of punishment.

179
00:10:34,050 --> 00:10:35,060
The Commandant of Justice also went to
Lane 3

180
00:10:35,060 --> 00:10:36,790
of Shanghe Ward to search and seal it,

181
00:10:36,790 --> 00:10:38,630
trying to catch those scholars
who had helped Liu Zhaolin

182
00:10:38,630 --> 00:10:40,490
forge the embezzlement ledgers.

183
00:10:40,670 --> 00:10:42,800
Unfortunately, he was a step too late.

184
00:10:45,540 --> 00:10:46,230
Also...

185
00:10:50,720 --> 00:10:51,480
Father,

186
00:10:52,490 --> 00:10:54,100
I only have one mother,

187
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,640
and that is Prince Qi's Consort.

188
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:58,320
Back then,
Prince Qi's Consort gave her life

189
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,890
in exchange for my sister's life and mine.

190
00:10:59,890 --> 00:11:01,490
I have never had a 2nd mother.

191
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:02,910
Avenging her

192
00:11:03,870 --> 00:11:05,120
is your obsession,

193
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:07,030
not mine.

194
00:11:21,430 --> 00:11:22,190
Hurry!

195
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,390
Did Liu Zhaolin mention

196
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:26,600
who gave him the orders before he died?

197
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:27,520
No.

198
00:11:27,580 --> 00:11:28,340
He didn't?

199
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:30,740
Liu Zhaolin's original surname was Pei.

200
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,960
He and He Yuanji, the former Heir's Consort
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

201
00:11:32,960 --> 00:11:34,270
were childhood sweethearts.

202
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:37,000
After He married into
Prince Jing'an's Mansion,

203
00:11:37,170 --> 00:11:38,930
he couldn't accept losing her,

204
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,510
so out of resentment,

205
00:11:40,630 --> 00:11:41,920
he deliberately framed them.

206
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:45,000
He even bribed the scholars
in Lane 3 of Shanghe Ward

207
00:11:45,510 --> 00:11:48,080
to forge the evidence
of corruption with him.

208
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:50,240
When the matter was exposed,

209
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,120
he committed suicide
to atone for his crimes

210
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:53,980
and clear the Xiao family's name.

211
00:11:54,080 --> 00:11:55,270
He was quite noble.

212
00:11:56,490 --> 00:12:00,880
[Court of Judicial Review]

213
00:12:06,870 --> 00:12:07,910
It's you?

214
00:12:09,030 --> 00:12:10,790
The moment I was imprisoned,

215
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,510
I was reminded of

216
00:12:13,140 --> 00:12:14,720
an old story that circulated

217
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,840
in the inner palace of the Capital.

218
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:20,120
When you used the collapse
of the grain canal

219
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:23,840
to try to wipe out
the entire Prince Jing'an's Household,

220
00:12:24,550 --> 00:12:26,550
it further confirmed my guess.

221
00:12:27,270 --> 00:12:30,320
The rumors about you
and Noble Concubine An back then

222
00:12:33,630 --> 00:12:34,390
were true.

223
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:42,150
Back then, you knew it was an unjust case,

224
00:12:42,150 --> 00:12:44,080
yet you still sent the two noble families—

225
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:46,540
hundreds of lives—to the execution ground.

226
00:12:46,590 --> 00:12:47,600
What I am doing now

227
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:49,480
is merely returning an eye for an eye.

228
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,360
Back then, the noble families
held absolute power.

229
00:12:51,360 --> 00:12:52,440
They defied the imperial authority

230
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,600
and oppressed the people,

231
00:12:53,600 --> 00:12:54,960
making life impossible for them

232
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:57,120
and leading rebel armies
to rise up everywhere.

233
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,670
So you could disregard right and wrong

234
00:12:58,670 --> 00:13:00,130
and kill innocent people?

235
00:13:00,150 --> 00:13:02,810
The An and Lu families
never committed treason!

236
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:05,650
Princess Pingning has been

237
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:09,920
secretly operating in the Capital
and has obtained solid evidence.

238
00:13:09,920 --> 00:13:11,450
In the An-Lu case back then,

239
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,670
you knew the truth

240
00:13:13,670 --> 00:13:14,870
but did not report it.

241
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,840
Oh, you, Xiao Ju.

242
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:21,960
You earned your title as Prince Jing'an

243
00:13:23,680 --> 00:13:25,800
on the blood of our noble families.

244
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,080
I admit

245
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,320
I am not innocent.

246
00:13:34,050 --> 00:13:35,510
But for the poor scholars,

247
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:37,870
for Emperor and Empress Wenxi,

248
00:13:37,870 --> 00:13:39,200
and even more, for Ye,

249
00:13:39,480 --> 00:13:41,550
I had to burn my boats.

250
00:13:42,750 --> 00:13:44,080
As for you, Grand Tutor,

251
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:46,910
as the head of the noble families,

252
00:13:48,030 --> 00:13:49,560
our stances are different.

253
00:13:50,510 --> 00:13:52,360
But speaking of wrongful deaths,

254
00:13:52,360 --> 00:13:53,440
to whom should those poor scholars

255
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:56,240
wrongfully killed
by the An and Lu families

256
00:13:57,410 --> 00:13:59,890
cry out for justice?

257
00:14:04,300 --> 00:14:08,660
If the An and Lu families
deserved to be punished

258
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:11,670
for overseeing
the waterway construction back then,

259
00:14:11,670 --> 00:14:14,720
then dare you say Xiao Yao
was entirely blameless

260
00:14:14,840 --> 00:14:19,150
for the collapse of the grain canal?

261
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:24,030
Is he really innocent?

262
00:14:32,910 --> 00:14:36,390
Corruption and smuggling
may have been false accusations,

263
00:14:37,250 --> 00:14:38,910
but the grain canal collapse—

264
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,290
I don't think so.

265
00:16:04,650 --> 00:16:05,910
Xiao Wuyi, you lied to me.

266
00:16:05,910 --> 00:16:07,000
You can see.

267
00:16:08,510 --> 00:16:10,360
This is called locating things by sound.

268
00:16:10,360 --> 00:16:12,670
I have been practicing it
for the past 2 years.

269
00:16:12,670 --> 00:16:14,080
Sooner or later, I will lose my sight.

270
00:16:14,080 --> 00:16:16,010
I can't be completely unprepared.

271
00:16:17,420 --> 00:16:18,820
Let go of me. Let me get up.

272
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,200
Let go!

273
00:16:26,270 --> 00:16:26,910
Xiao Wuyi.

274
00:16:27,270 --> 00:16:29,070
Why didn't you tell me 2 years ago

275
00:16:29,480 --> 00:16:32,140
that the blood stasis
would keep getting worse?

276
00:16:32,570 --> 00:16:35,140
You are cruel,
planning to leave me behind.

277
00:16:35,570 --> 00:16:37,120
Aren't you afraid I'll back out?

278
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,650
What can you do? Divorce me?

279
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:41,610
After all, you've already burned
the divorce paper.

280
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:46,630
You...

281
00:16:55,910 --> 00:16:56,970
Why are you crying?

282
00:17:02,870 --> 00:17:04,680
This blood stasis cannot be cured.

283
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:05,880
Even if I had told you,

284
00:17:06,270 --> 00:17:08,270
it would have only added to your worries.

285
00:17:08,270 --> 00:17:09,930
But if you had told me earlier,

286
00:17:10,270 --> 00:17:12,670
I wouldn't have left you
in the past 2 years.

287
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:15,290
And I wouldn't have been so oblivious,

288
00:17:16,069 --> 00:17:18,130
thinking we still had plenty of time.

289
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,349
Alright.

290
00:17:26,790 --> 00:17:30,250
These past 2 years you've been
following the map to find mines,

291
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:32,470
traveling thousands of miles

292
00:17:32,470 --> 00:17:34,870
and seeing the world
and all living beings.

293
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:37,200
You opened branches
of Miraculous Craft across Ye

294
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:38,310
to help the people.

295
00:17:39,590 --> 00:17:40,920
Are you happy?

296
00:17:48,790 --> 00:17:51,250
Your happiness
is the most important thing.

297
00:17:56,830 --> 00:17:58,720
Xiao Wuyi, I'm telling you.

298
00:17:59,440 --> 00:18:00,640
I haven't finished burning

299
00:18:00,640 --> 00:18:01,700
the divorce paper.

300
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:02,880
There's still half left.

301
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:03,750
If you ever

302
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:05,030
hide anything

303
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:05,830
from me again,

304
00:18:06,400 --> 00:18:07,920
anyone who wants to be the Heir's Consort
can have the title.

305
00:18:07,920 --> 00:18:09,320
I'm not doing it anymore.

306
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:15,350
Trying to trick me? You want to back out?

307
00:18:17,110 --> 00:18:17,970
My blueprints!

308
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:21,110
Xiao Wuyi, you can see.

309
00:18:24,310 --> 00:18:25,000
I can't see.

310
00:18:34,830 --> 00:18:36,790
Ziqi, listen to me.

311
00:18:37,110 --> 00:18:37,880
If you ever meet

312
00:18:37,880 --> 00:18:39,440
someone like your father,

313
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,510
stay away from him,

314
00:18:40,690 --> 00:18:42,290
or he'll ruin your good name.

315
00:18:42,510 --> 00:18:44,640
What kind of person is he?

316
00:18:45,810 --> 00:18:47,240
To coax a lady,

317
00:18:47,550 --> 00:18:49,480
he calls a terminal illness a cold.

318
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:50,880
He doesn't take care of himself

319
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:52,750
and refuses
to take his condition seriously.

320
00:18:52,750 --> 00:18:53,830
But Mother,

321
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:56,730
I don't want to study medicine
in the future.

322
00:18:56,830 --> 00:18:57,880
Then what do you want to study?

323
00:18:57,880 --> 00:18:59,200
I want to study poison.

324
00:19:00,110 --> 00:19:01,000
Say that again.

325
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:04,260
I also want to learn Auntie Jiayu's
mechanical skills.

326
00:19:04,310 --> 00:19:06,110
If I can combine the two of them,

327
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,670
it will be very powerful.

328
00:19:07,830 --> 00:19:09,880
That day, I even saw...

329
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:12,720
Mother, have mercy!

330
00:19:14,300 --> 00:19:15,780
Duan Ziqi, come back here!

331
00:19:16,110 --> 00:19:17,920
Hang out less with your Auntie Jiayu!

332
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:19,750
If you dare to touch her alchemy furnace,

333
00:19:19,750 --> 00:19:21,150
I'll chop off your hands!

334
00:19:21,440 --> 00:19:22,110
See?

335
00:19:22,750 --> 00:19:24,210
What have you taught Ziqi?

336
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,570
It's clearly you who refuses to let go.

337
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,240
What is this?

338
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:34,170
This is a cane I made for you.

339
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:36,570
It has a mechanism inside.

340
00:19:37,550 --> 00:19:40,410
It can be retracted into your sleeve
when not in use.

341
00:19:40,590 --> 00:19:42,240
But you've learned
to locate things by sound.

342
00:19:42,240 --> 00:19:43,640
I don't think you need it.

343
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:45,040
Who says I don't?

344
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:49,270
Xie Jiayu.

345
00:19:51,830 --> 00:19:54,890
Actually, the divorce paper
I wrote in prison was fake.

346
00:19:57,030 --> 00:19:58,690
I never wanted to divorce you.

347
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:03,070
I know.

348
00:20:04,270 --> 00:20:05,270
Two years ago,

349
00:20:05,790 --> 00:20:06,920
Ruisheng told me

350
00:20:08,160 --> 00:20:10,400
there was a way to clear my blood stasis,

351
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:11,880
but it was very risky.

352
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:14,110
If it failed,

353
00:20:15,680 --> 00:20:17,480
I could lose my life at any time.

354
00:20:20,590 --> 00:20:22,050
But for the sake of reform,

355
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:24,650
I chose not to take that chance.

356
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:27,880
I'm sorry.

357
00:20:28,510 --> 00:20:29,880
Call me selfish

358
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,280
or shameless.

359
00:20:33,030 --> 00:20:35,430
Even knowing
that I am destined to fail you,

360
00:20:38,030 --> 00:20:39,350
I will never let you go.

361
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:46,440
If Ruisheng knows
you're not resting properly

362
00:20:46,440 --> 00:20:48,240
and that you're shedding tears,

363
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:49,660
she'll scold me again.

364
00:20:51,110 --> 00:20:52,170
She wouldn't dare.

365
00:20:53,590 --> 00:20:55,050
You are my Heir's Consort.

366
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:03,750
I lost my parents when I was young.

367
00:21:04,880 --> 00:21:05,550
Mother,

368
00:21:06,340 --> 00:21:07,070
Grand Tutor,

369
00:21:07,320 --> 00:21:08,590
Lejun, and Mao

370
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,590
have also left me one by one.

371
00:21:13,550 --> 00:21:14,440
My whole life,

372
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:18,150
it seems I've been learning
how to say goodbye.

373
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:22,200
So don't worry.

374
00:21:24,500 --> 00:21:26,300
I am very good at saying goodbye.

375
00:21:29,480 --> 00:21:31,080
Even if that day really comes

376
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,400
and you leave me,

377
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:38,030
I will cry for you for a month at most.

378
00:21:40,790 --> 00:21:42,480
No, 3 months.

379
00:21:49,250 --> 00:21:51,180
As long as you promise me one thing,

380
00:21:53,490 --> 00:21:55,490
you won't be breaking your promise.

381
00:21:57,270 --> 00:21:57,880
Alright?

382
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:02,200
Tell me.

383
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:06,880
Whether it is 3 years

384
00:22:07,680 --> 00:22:08,680
or 5 years,

385
00:22:10,270 --> 00:22:11,400
from today on,

386
00:22:12,350 --> 00:22:14,550
forget the deadline Ruisheng gave you.

387
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:16,550
No matter when,

388
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:21,660
as long as you remember
that I am waiting for you,

389
00:22:22,310 --> 00:22:23,510
can you hold on for me

390
00:22:24,640 --> 00:22:26,160
for as long as you can?

391
00:22:27,110 --> 00:22:28,270
Let's go as far

392
00:22:28,270 --> 00:22:29,330
as we can together.

393
00:22:31,940 --> 00:22:33,600
I only need you to do your best,

394
00:22:34,330 --> 00:22:35,660
and I will do my best too.

395
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:40,980
Then I won't see it
as you letting me down.

396
00:22:41,920 --> 00:22:43,580
But 3 months is just too short.

397
00:22:44,750 --> 00:22:46,010
It really is too short.

398
00:22:47,270 --> 00:22:48,440
How about 3 years?

399
00:22:49,110 --> 00:22:50,310
Forget me

400
00:22:52,590 --> 00:22:53,990
3 years after I die, okay?

401
00:22:54,550 --> 00:22:56,550
Can't you just say you will try harder

402
00:22:56,550 --> 00:22:57,790
to stay alive?

403
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:05,070
Okay.

404
00:23:18,270 --> 00:23:21,180
Rest assured. Although His Highness
doesn't care about his life,

405
00:23:21,180 --> 00:23:22,250
as a physician,

406
00:23:22,280 --> 00:23:24,140
I still care about my reputation.

407
00:23:24,240 --> 00:23:26,640
I will do everything I can
to keep him alive.

408
00:23:32,110 --> 00:23:33,310
Thank you, Ruisheng.

409
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,830
Fortunately, with you here now,

410
00:23:36,830 --> 00:23:39,230
my chances of success are actually higher.

411
00:23:40,550 --> 00:23:42,750
But he has put off treatment for so long.

412
00:23:44,600 --> 00:23:46,080
Life is truly magical.

413
00:23:46,830 --> 00:23:49,680
Sometimes, the will to live
matters more than anything else.

414
00:23:49,680 --> 00:23:52,210
In my eyes, Xiao Wuyi,
the commander of Beifu,

415
00:23:52,290 --> 00:23:53,940
was once more like

416
00:23:54,400 --> 00:23:55,730
a cold lifeless weapon.

417
00:23:56,480 --> 00:23:58,760
He gave almost everything for this world.

418
00:23:58,760 --> 00:24:01,350
He clearly took the world
as his responsibility,

419
00:24:01,350 --> 00:24:02,480
but it seemed

420
00:24:02,790 --> 00:24:05,720
he had never been attached
to anything in this world.

421
00:24:07,070 --> 00:24:08,020
Until he met you.

422
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:14,750
People with aspirations cling to life,

423
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:16,080
and martyrs seek death.

424
00:24:18,230 --> 00:24:18,990
Jiayu.

425
00:24:20,160 --> 00:24:21,420
You must hold onto him.

426
00:24:41,610 --> 00:24:43,410
You know your days are numbered.

427
00:24:43,440 --> 00:24:45,350
Five or ten years

428
00:24:45,830 --> 00:24:48,290
won't be enough
to complete your grand plan.

429
00:24:48,800 --> 00:24:52,200
That's why you're in such a rush
to complete the Beifu Reform.

430
00:24:54,030 --> 00:24:55,160
These past few days,

431
00:24:55,340 --> 00:24:56,720
I've been reading the military strategies
and essays

432
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:57,850
you wrote in prison.

433
00:24:58,470 --> 00:24:59,920
You knew my background

434
00:24:59,940 --> 00:25:01,050
but said nothing,

435
00:25:01,270 --> 00:25:02,070
because you were certain

436
00:25:02,070 --> 00:25:03,830
that I would eventually agree with you.

437
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:05,510
You were also certain I would march north,

438
00:25:05,510 --> 00:25:06,240
weren't you?

439
00:25:08,440 --> 00:25:09,880
Over 20 years have passed.

440
00:25:09,880 --> 00:25:10,830
How many survivors of Ye

441
00:25:10,830 --> 00:25:12,350
are being treated like cattle and slaves
by Northern Qin

442
00:25:12,350 --> 00:25:14,410
on the lands that once belonged to Ye?

443
00:25:14,640 --> 00:25:15,310
To this day,

444
00:25:15,310 --> 00:25:17,910
they are still waiting for
Crown Prince Wenxi.

445
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:20,550
But what about 30 or 40 years from now?

446
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:24,870
Yizhi, you are different
from the Grand Tutor.

447
00:25:25,390 --> 00:25:26,480
The noble families don't care about
reclaiming our land

448
00:25:26,480 --> 00:25:28,200
and are content to indulge in pleasure.

449
00:25:28,200 --> 00:25:29,030
But Prince Qi

450
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:31,780
will never forget the fall of Qizhou.

451
00:25:32,530 --> 00:25:33,770
But I am not a pawn!

452
00:25:35,680 --> 00:25:37,720
My life and honor

453
00:25:38,200 --> 00:25:38,960
must never depend on

454
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:40,510
your passing whims!

455
00:25:42,310 --> 00:25:43,750
Prince Jing'an's Household

456
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:44,750
and the Beifu Army

457
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,880
must both be contained!

458
00:25:47,550 --> 00:25:49,750
Are you counting on the noble families?

459
00:25:50,790 --> 00:25:52,240
You know better than I do

460
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:54,810
that they are the true blight of Ye.

461
00:25:57,310 --> 00:25:58,000
Yizhi,

462
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:01,400
if you rule your people
through manipulation,

463
00:26:01,400 --> 00:26:03,400
they will manipulate you in return.

464
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:04,530
Why not

465
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:06,920
try another way?

466
00:26:12,310 --> 00:26:15,160
Bravo! Bravo!

467
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,400
Bravo!

468
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,260
Where is the money?

469
00:26:22,830 --> 00:26:23,350
Where is my money?

470
00:26:23,350 --> 00:26:24,480
Listen, brat.

471
00:26:24,540 --> 00:26:26,270
You are not leaving today without paying.

472
00:26:26,270 --> 00:26:26,960
Give us the money!

473
00:26:26,960 --> 00:26:27,930
Give us the money!

474
00:26:27,930 --> 00:26:30,060
-Give us the money!
-Behave yourself!

475
00:26:31,600 --> 00:26:34,000
You should've done that earlier. Let's go.

476
00:26:43,520 --> 00:26:45,070
Mao, I am hungry.

477
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:55,560
Thank you.

478
00:27:01,920 --> 00:27:02,590
Move!

479
00:27:02,750 --> 00:27:03,640
Out of the way!

480
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:08,640
Xiao Wuyi,

481
00:27:08,790 --> 00:27:11,270
so many refugees are begging
outside Jiankang.

482
00:27:11,270 --> 00:27:13,270
Why is the Beifu Army doing nothing?

483
00:27:14,190 --> 00:27:15,240
Have you ever thought about

484
00:27:15,240 --> 00:27:17,240
what Ye will be like in the future?

485
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:21,270
I hope for a Ye of peace and prosperity,

486
00:27:21,790 --> 00:27:24,440
with capable generals
defending the borders,

487
00:27:24,790 --> 00:27:26,920
a righteous and well-governed court,

488
00:27:27,030 --> 00:27:31,430
and scholars of both noble and humble origins
making full use of their talents.

489
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:49,270
They are the scholars of humble origins
hiding in Xiyuan.

490
00:27:50,030 --> 00:27:51,030
Why were Liu Zhaolin and those

491
00:27:51,030 --> 00:27:52,760
poor scholars hiding in Xiyuan

492
00:27:53,560 --> 00:27:55,160
willing to help Xie Huaigui?

493
00:27:55,440 --> 00:27:56,570
It's simply because

494
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:59,440
relying on the powerful is their only path
to an official career.

495
00:27:59,440 --> 00:28:01,850
If not forced by circumstances,

496
00:28:02,360 --> 00:28:05,690
what scholar would willingly
soil their brush and clothes?

497
00:28:11,410 --> 00:28:12,000
Tell me.

498
00:28:13,590 --> 00:28:15,520
Should I give them another chance?

499
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:17,600
Your Highness saved my life.

500
00:28:18,120 --> 00:28:19,160
To me,

501
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,440
Your Highness

502
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:23,380
is a god who guided my soul
through the darkness.

503
00:28:23,590 --> 00:28:24,350
If today,

504
00:28:24,570 --> 00:28:26,720
Your Highness is willing
to give them another chance,

505
00:28:26,720 --> 00:28:28,210
they will surely
dedicate their entire lives

506
00:28:28,210 --> 00:28:29,380
to you.

507
00:28:33,750 --> 00:28:36,030
Forgive me, Your Highness. I misspoke.

508
00:28:45,380 --> 00:28:46,840
Get them some new clothes.

509
00:28:47,250 --> 00:28:47,860
Yes.

510
00:28:53,750 --> 00:28:55,350
We can establish the Nine-Rank System,

511
00:28:55,350 --> 00:28:59,440
with family background,
literary talent, and moral conduct

512
00:28:59,830 --> 00:29:01,310
as the criteria for ranking.

513
00:29:01,310 --> 00:29:03,550
Only nobles
can attain the upper ranks.

514
00:29:03,600 --> 00:29:07,330
You still see the Lantai gathering
as a private tool for the nobles.

515
00:29:07,920 --> 00:29:09,120
I have been Regent for 3 years.

516
00:29:09,120 --> 00:29:10,680
I established provincial schools

517
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:12,080
and expanded libraries.

518
00:29:12,370 --> 00:29:15,110
Talents from humble origins
are no longer what they once were.

519
00:29:15,110 --> 00:29:15,770
Therefore,

520
00:29:16,590 --> 00:29:19,530
I will change the Lantai gathering
into spring examinations,

521
00:29:19,530 --> 00:29:22,830
letting the commoners and nobles
compete on equal footing.

522
00:29:22,830 --> 00:29:26,590
Your Highness, the hierarchy of rites
is like a guiding star.

523
00:29:26,720 --> 00:29:28,880
If old systems are recklessly changed,

524
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:31,610
I fear the order of the realm
will fall into chaos.

525
00:29:33,070 --> 00:29:35,730
Master, you have helped me
reach this position.

526
00:29:36,270 --> 00:29:39,600
What's the point of talking about
the order of the realm now?

527
00:29:42,070 --> 00:29:45,640
Your Highness, holding a spring exam
requires massive effort.

528
00:29:46,270 --> 00:29:48,400
Moreover, the children of noble families

529
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:50,270
have studied the classics since childhood.

530
00:29:50,270 --> 00:29:52,440
The great scholars are all at our schools.

531
00:29:52,440 --> 00:29:53,440
And the academies

532
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:56,530
are all operated
by the major noble families.

533
00:29:57,030 --> 00:29:59,640
They spend fortunes to gather the wise

534
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:03,030
and have already recruited
all the elite of the realm.

535
00:30:04,030 --> 00:30:04,880
Could it be

536
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:08,530
that you are afraid the nobles
can't beat the humble scholars?

537
00:30:10,070 --> 00:30:12,830
If Your Highness insists on doing this,

538
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:15,550
I have one condition.

539
00:30:16,270 --> 00:30:19,880
Pose a challenging question
for all students and have them discuss

540
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:23,210
the difficulties and solutions
in waterway construction.

541
00:30:23,570 --> 00:30:25,480
This is a universal challenge.

542
00:30:26,190 --> 00:30:29,400
Let's see which of the two groups,
the nobles and the humble scholars,

543
00:30:29,400 --> 00:30:31,600
truly understands Ye's state affairs.

544
00:30:32,960 --> 00:30:34,560
If, as Your Highness claims,

545
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:37,670
the nobles can't beat the humble scholars,

546
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,720
I am willing to retire,

547
00:30:40,020 --> 00:30:41,080
reopen my academy,

548
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:42,350
devote myself to scholarship,

549
00:30:42,350 --> 00:30:45,080
and no longer
get involved in political affairs.

550
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:47,460
You must be joking.

551
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,310
I approve of this.

552
00:30:53,550 --> 00:30:54,790
[Imperial Academy]

553
00:30:55,790 --> 00:30:57,070
The time for this year's Lantai gathering
has been set.

554
00:30:57,070 --> 00:30:58,310
What? When?

555
00:30:58,310 --> 00:30:59,030
When? Let me see.

556
00:30:59,030 --> 00:30:59,790
Wait.

557
00:31:02,710 --> 00:31:03,960
By order of the Eastern Palace,

558
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:06,290
this year's Lantai gathering is canceled

559
00:31:06,510 --> 00:31:07,750
and replaced by a spring examination.

560
00:31:07,750 --> 00:31:09,000
Talents will be selected

561
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,930
regardless of family background.

562
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:11,920
Regardless of family background?

563
00:31:11,920 --> 00:31:15,000
-Canceled? A spring examination?
-Regardless of family background?

564
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:16,640
It's an order from the Eastern Palace?

565
00:31:16,640 --> 00:31:17,440
Xie Huaigui!

566
00:31:17,590 --> 00:31:19,790
Xie Huaigui, come out!

567
00:31:19,790 --> 00:31:21,400
Why is the Lantai gathering canceled?

568
00:31:21,400 --> 00:31:23,640
Why is it canceled?
Why set a spring examination?

569
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:25,400
-Xie Huaigui!
-Xie Huaigui!

570
00:31:25,750 --> 00:31:26,750
Come out!

571
00:31:27,580 --> 00:31:28,200
Return to the mansion.

572
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:29,000
Why is it canceled?

573
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:30,000
Xie Huaigui!

574
00:31:30,650 --> 00:31:32,650
The spring exam will start in 3 days.

575
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:35,180
Your brother spends all day
reading storybooks.

576
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:36,740
His heart lies not here,

577
00:31:36,850 --> 00:31:38,720
but among the mountains and rivers.

578
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:40,550
He frequents music houses all day.

579
00:31:40,550 --> 00:31:41,750
The gazette says

580
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,070
this examination

581
00:31:43,070 --> 00:31:45,720
only has 2 subjects:
Confucian classics and policy essays.

582
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:47,550
Students take the exam anonymously,

583
00:31:47,550 --> 00:31:48,750
and papers are graded anonymously.

584
00:31:48,750 --> 00:31:50,240
Five matches are ranked as superior,

585
00:31:50,240 --> 00:31:51,750
three or four as middle,

586
00:31:51,880 --> 00:31:53,010
and two as inferior.

587
00:31:53,750 --> 00:31:55,480
I don't know if it's true or not.

588
00:31:55,480 --> 00:31:56,400
Yuanji.

589
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,110
You are now

590
00:31:58,110 --> 00:31:59,920
the head of our He family.

591
00:32:00,100 --> 00:32:01,480
If your father and brother

592
00:32:01,480 --> 00:32:02,960
fail to secure a good future,

593
00:32:02,960 --> 00:32:05,370
who in the entire He family

594
00:32:05,400 --> 00:32:06,800
will truly submit to you?

595
00:32:07,160 --> 00:32:09,830
Yuanji! Did you hear me?

596
00:32:09,830 --> 00:32:12,230
You need to talk to your father
and brother.

597
00:32:13,080 --> 00:32:14,420
Throughout history, talent selection

598
00:32:14,420 --> 00:32:16,790
has always been based on
family background.

599
00:32:16,790 --> 00:32:18,380
As the saying goes, those of humble origins
cannot reach high ranks,

600
00:32:18,380 --> 00:32:19,680
and those from noble families
do not fall to low ranks.

601
00:32:19,680 --> 00:32:21,250
Prince Qi has now
set a spring examination.

602
00:32:21,250 --> 00:32:22,320
Regardless of noble or humble status,

603
00:32:22,320 --> 00:32:23,190
or connections,

604
00:32:23,190 --> 00:32:24,480
as long as one has real talent,

605
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:25,740
they can take the exam.

606
00:32:26,310 --> 00:32:28,310
If they truly appoint officials
based on ability,

607
00:32:28,310 --> 00:32:29,440
it would be a great achievement.

608
00:32:29,440 --> 00:32:30,920
But they are unwilling to take the exam.

609
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:32,310
What's the point?

610
00:32:34,290 --> 00:32:35,090
Auntie He.

611
00:32:39,940 --> 00:32:40,820
Don't worry.

612
00:32:41,120 --> 00:32:42,780
I have come up with a good idea.

613
00:32:43,110 --> 00:32:45,510
Isn't the path forward for the He family

614
00:32:45,650 --> 00:32:46,850
right in front of you?

615
00:32:47,350 --> 00:32:48,240
Your Highness,

616
00:32:48,450 --> 00:32:50,300
are you making fun of us?

617
00:32:52,050 --> 00:32:52,770
Yuanji,

618
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:54,190
think about it.

619
00:32:54,430 --> 00:32:56,030
I'm serious about this.

620
00:32:56,050 --> 00:32:58,450
Yuanji, don't listen to her nonsense.

621
00:32:58,640 --> 00:33:00,100
It could cost us our lives.

622
00:33:01,270 --> 00:33:02,130
Your Highness,

623
00:33:02,590 --> 00:33:03,590
please go back.

624
00:33:04,550 --> 00:33:05,030
Please go back.

625
00:33:05,030 --> 00:33:05,680
Yuanji,

626
00:33:05,680 --> 00:33:06,750
I am serious.

627
00:33:06,750 --> 00:33:07,640
Think about it.

628
00:33:49,980 --> 00:33:51,750
[Prince Jing'an's Mansion]

629
00:33:55,750 --> 00:33:57,320
You are making me dizzy.

630
00:33:58,270 --> 00:34:00,870
I wonder what rank Yuanji received
in the exam.

631
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:02,570
The results are out!

632
00:34:05,200 --> 00:34:05,880
The results are out?

633
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:06,510
Yes.

634
00:34:06,680 --> 00:34:07,200
What rank?

635
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:07,860
First rank.

636
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:08,590
Really?

637
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:10,510
Now Yuanji

638
00:34:10,510 --> 00:34:12,110
can finally hold her head high.

639
00:34:12,110 --> 00:34:13,110
She is a female Academician now

640
00:34:13,110 --> 00:34:14,969
and will become a court official.

641
00:34:14,969 --> 00:34:16,170
I need to design

642
00:34:16,199 --> 00:34:18,000
a ceremonial hairpiece for her.

643
00:34:18,030 --> 00:34:18,960
Where is she now?

644
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:20,760
She has entered the Eastern Palace

645
00:34:20,760 --> 00:34:22,760
and is about to be granted the title.

646
00:34:26,030 --> 00:34:28,110
He Yuan,
the second child of the fifth branch

647
00:34:28,110 --> 00:34:29,920
of the He family in Yingchuan,

648
00:34:29,940 --> 00:34:32,360
topped the list
in this imperial examination.

649
00:34:32,360 --> 00:34:33,590
He can enter the Imperial Academy

650
00:34:33,590 --> 00:34:34,960
with the title of Academician,

651
00:34:34,960 --> 00:34:37,080
ranked Upper First Grade.

652
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:39,530
He Yuan, the second child of the fifth branch
of the He family in Yingchuan,

653
00:34:39,530 --> 00:34:40,590
pays her respects.

654
00:34:44,679 --> 00:34:45,360
Rise.

655
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:49,570
Thank you, Your Highness.

656
00:34:59,000 --> 00:34:59,800
Wait.

657
00:35:13,650 --> 00:35:15,050
May I ask, Your Highness,

658
00:35:15,710 --> 00:35:17,640
why you specifically chose He Yuan

659
00:35:17,710 --> 00:35:19,880
as the top Academician
in the spring examination?

660
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:21,030
Is it because of the question about

661
00:35:21,030 --> 00:35:24,360
the difficulties and solutions
in waterway construction?

662
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:25,970
You're right, Grand Tutor.

663
00:35:26,240 --> 00:35:27,230
For this question,

664
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:28,800
all examinees quoted the late Emperor's

665
00:35:28,800 --> 00:35:31,200
"Wenxi Treatise" on waterway management,

666
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:34,280
using wooden stakes and wicker
to reinforce the riverbanks.

667
00:35:34,280 --> 00:35:36,670
But He Yuan proposed

668
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:39,120
the method of bamboo cage with pebbles.

669
00:35:39,180 --> 00:35:40,980
He Yuan, explain it to everyone.

670
00:35:44,590 --> 00:35:46,030
The method of bamboo cage with pebbles

671
00:35:46,030 --> 00:35:47,320
means weaving bamboo into cages,

672
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:50,030
filling them with pebbles,
and sinking them into the river.

673
00:35:50,030 --> 00:35:52,320
The toughness of bamboo cages
and the weight of the pebbles

674
00:35:52,320 --> 00:35:53,740
can both stabilize the riverbank

675
00:35:53,740 --> 00:35:55,880
and withstand the impact
of the water flow.

676
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:57,630
This is a method of overcoming
hardness with softness.

677
00:35:57,630 --> 00:35:59,710
Let me ask you.
How did you, a child of a noble family,

678
00:35:59,710 --> 00:36:01,170
come to know the solution?

679
00:36:01,200 --> 00:36:02,110
Your Highness,

680
00:36:02,630 --> 00:36:04,880
I learned this from a criminal.

681
00:36:05,310 --> 00:36:06,100
A criminal?

682
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:07,320
A criminal?

683
00:36:07,320 --> 00:36:09,320
I brought him here today.

684
00:36:09,730 --> 00:36:10,560
His name is...

685
00:36:11,440 --> 00:36:13,070
Liu Zhaolin.

686
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,920
I'm Liu Zhaolin, a criminal.

687
00:36:32,110 --> 00:36:33,370
Greetings, Prince Qi.

688
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:35,150
Liu Zhaolin?

689
00:36:36,820 --> 00:36:38,050
Aren't you dead?

690
00:36:38,930 --> 00:36:40,160
Grand Tutor wanted me

691
00:36:40,190 --> 00:36:41,240
to die in the Court of Judicial Review,

692
00:36:41,240 --> 00:36:42,840
but Young Lord Xiao saved me.

693
00:36:43,730 --> 00:36:45,660
I met Grand Tutor in the bookstore.

694
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,840
He said that if I wanted to stand out,

695
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:49,640
I must first learn to bow my head.

696
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:50,880
As long as I forged the account books

697
00:36:50,880 --> 00:36:52,420
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion for him,

698
00:36:52,420 --> 00:36:54,710
framing their family
for colluding with foreign enemies,

699
00:36:54,710 --> 00:36:57,570
he would give me a chance
to enter official service.

700
00:36:57,720 --> 00:36:58,840
So I bowed my head.

701
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:00,670
I deceived the former Heir's Consort

702
00:37:00,670 --> 00:37:02,270
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion

703
00:37:02,430 --> 00:37:05,280
and tricked her into giving me
the Xiaos' private letters.

704
00:37:05,280 --> 00:37:07,260
In Lane 3 of Shanghe Ward, a place
arranged by the Grand Tutor,

705
00:37:07,260 --> 00:37:09,120
I spent 3 whole months practicing

706
00:37:09,710 --> 00:37:10,670
until my forged handwriting

707
00:37:10,670 --> 00:37:12,350
was convincing enough to pass as genuine.

708
00:37:12,350 --> 00:37:15,660
But later, when the case
of Prince Jing'an's Mansion broke out,

709
00:37:15,660 --> 00:37:16,990
he wanted to silence me.

710
00:37:18,540 --> 00:37:19,730
I saw the method
of bamboo cage with pebbles

711
00:37:19,730 --> 00:37:21,560
in the Grand Tutor's study.

712
00:37:22,420 --> 00:37:25,340
He has been studying
this method for over a decade.

713
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,550
Yes, I was the one who ordered

714
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:31,920
Liu Zhaolin and others to fabricate

715
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:34,550
the charges
against Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

716
00:37:34,550 --> 00:37:36,280
And I have indeed been studying

717
00:37:36,280 --> 00:37:37,920
the method of bamboo cage with pebbles.

718
00:37:37,920 --> 00:37:39,070
But do you know

719
00:37:39,070 --> 00:37:41,070
the origin of this method?

720
00:37:42,130 --> 00:37:43,520
Back then, the An and Lu families

721
00:37:43,520 --> 00:37:46,890
used exactly this method
for waterway management.

722
00:37:47,610 --> 00:37:50,320
But at that time,
this method was framed as evidence

723
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:52,150
that the An and Lu families
had deliberately damaged the waterways

724
00:37:52,150 --> 00:37:53,480
and colluded with Northern Qin.

725
00:37:53,480 --> 00:37:54,630
They were charged with treason.

726
00:37:54,630 --> 00:37:56,000
As a result, for over 20 years,

727
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:57,600
no one dared use this method.

728
00:37:58,030 --> 00:38:00,490
If Your Highness acknowledges this method,

729
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:03,480
that would prove that Emperor Wenxi
was mistaken

730
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:06,740
and that the An and Lu families
were wrongfully convicted!

731
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:13,000
Brother.

732
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:20,730
The model of the bamboo cage with pebbles?

733
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,230
Xiao Wuyi,

734
00:38:22,260 --> 00:38:25,790
you knew all along that Brother and I
were studying this method?

735
00:38:26,570 --> 00:38:27,770
Everything is ready.

736
00:38:32,300 --> 00:38:33,010
Xiao Wuyi,

737
00:38:33,550 --> 00:38:36,750
are you going to clear
the An and Lu families' names today?

738
00:38:37,410 --> 00:38:38,180
If so,

739
00:38:38,320 --> 00:38:39,920
I'm afraid the posthumous reputations
of Emperor and Empress Wenxi

740
00:38:39,920 --> 00:38:41,120
cannot be preserved.

741
00:38:42,070 --> 00:38:43,070
I don't care about

742
00:38:43,320 --> 00:38:44,180
the Grand Tutor

743
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:45,190
or the past.

744
00:38:45,510 --> 00:38:48,230
What I care about
is how to construct the waterways,

745
00:38:48,230 --> 00:38:49,630
how to save the people

746
00:38:49,840 --> 00:38:51,400
from the suffering of floods,

747
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:53,380
and how to open the grain canal
to the Northern Border as soon as possible.

748
00:38:53,380 --> 00:38:54,710
If this method is right,

749
00:38:54,880 --> 00:38:56,210
it shouldn't be buried.

750
00:38:57,030 --> 00:38:57,840
Xie Jiayu,

751
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:00,460
are you willing to help me?

752
00:39:03,470 --> 00:39:06,360
The case of the An and Lu families' treason
has long been settled.

753
00:39:06,360 --> 00:39:08,690
And this method
of bamboo cages with pebbles

754
00:39:08,690 --> 00:39:10,620
has not been used for over 20 years.

755
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,320
Then how can we prove

756
00:39:12,590 --> 00:39:14,630
whether this method works or not?

757
00:39:17,510 --> 00:39:19,240
Then please allow me the chance

758
00:39:19,670 --> 00:39:21,880
to prove it today in the Eastern Palace.

759
00:39:24,320 --> 00:39:26,850
I, Xiao Yao,
pay my respects to Your Highness.

760
00:39:46,550 --> 00:39:47,960
I, Xiao Yao, a disgraced subject,

761
00:39:47,960 --> 00:39:49,820
pay my respects to Your Highness.

762
00:39:51,500 --> 00:39:52,890
Ever since the waterway collapsed,

763
00:39:52,890 --> 00:39:54,620
I have not slept a single night.

764
00:39:55,120 --> 00:39:56,750
Fortunately,
I received guidance from Mr. Liu,

765
00:39:56,750 --> 00:39:58,510
and with the help of the Heir's Consort,

766
00:39:58,510 --> 00:40:00,250
I crafted this bamboo cage with pebbles.

767
00:40:00,250 --> 00:40:03,230
I humbly ask Your Highness
to grant permission for a trial.

768
00:40:03,230 --> 00:40:04,360
Permission granted.

769
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:05,820
Thank you, Your Highness.

770
00:40:09,580 --> 00:40:10,310
Assemble it.

771
00:40:12,370 --> 00:40:12,970
Add water.

772
00:40:48,390 --> 00:40:49,720
The pebbles in this cage

773
00:40:49,960 --> 00:40:52,760
must be 70% angular stones
and 30% rounded stones,

774
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:55,360
with the stones arranged
from the bottom up in a spiral shape.

775
00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:56,690
The 3rd piece is the key.

776
00:40:57,230 --> 00:40:58,760
If a fully round one is used,

777
00:40:58,960 --> 00:41:01,490
the water will disperse
like a defeated army.

778
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,030
It's done.

779
00:41:12,830 --> 00:41:14,480
Look, the water flow has slowed down.

780
00:41:14,480 --> 00:41:16,010
The house didn't collapse.

781
00:41:20,150 --> 00:41:22,080
I wonder if what you have seen today

782
00:41:22,330 --> 00:41:24,860
can untie the knot in your heart,
Grand Tutor.

783
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:36,620
Your Highness.

784
00:41:37,360 --> 00:41:39,810
If we don't correct
Emperor Wenxi's mistake today,

785
00:41:39,810 --> 00:41:41,360
I'm sure more people

786
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:42,960
will suffer from the floods.

787
00:41:43,230 --> 00:41:46,860
Your Highness, please give your judgment.

788
00:41:54,800 --> 00:41:57,540
Back then,
to seize power from the noble families,

789
00:41:57,540 --> 00:41:58,550
Emperor Wenxi used
the waterway construction case as a pretext

790
00:41:58,550 --> 00:42:01,030
to frame the An and Lu families
for colluding with Northern Qin.

791
00:42:01,030 --> 00:42:03,490
It plunged Ye
into endless internal strife,

792
00:42:03,680 --> 00:42:06,550
allowing Northern Qin to take the opportunity
to march south and overrun the Capital.

793
00:42:06,550 --> 00:42:09,880
This tragedy was single-handedly
caused by Emperor Wenxi,

794
00:42:10,030 --> 00:42:12,070
and it was a disaster born from the conflict between
the noble families and the common people.

795
00:42:12,070 --> 00:42:14,150
If we do not abandon the divide
between nobles and commoners

796
00:42:14,150 --> 00:42:16,280
and clear the names
of the An and Lu families,

797
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:19,280
the tragedy of the Capital
will surely repeat itself.

798
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:23,100
Emperor and Empress Wenxi were not gods,

799
00:42:23,340 --> 00:42:24,230
and the world should not be defined

800
00:42:24,230 --> 00:42:26,000
only by the divide
between nobles and commoners.

801
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:29,000
Above all, the world cannot depend
on a single person.

802
00:42:29,230 --> 00:42:30,590
And that person in your hearts,

803
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:32,450
the god-like Crown Prince Wenxi,

804
00:42:33,360 --> 00:42:34,150
actually

805
00:42:35,560 --> 00:42:38,000
died long ago on his way south
to Jiankang.

806
00:42:57,480 --> 00:42:58,480
Pass on my decree.

807
00:42:59,050 --> 00:43:01,310
Clear the names of the An and Lu families.

808
00:43:01,890 --> 00:43:03,280
All false charges against them

809
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:04,410
shall be dismissed.

810
00:43:04,880 --> 00:43:06,140
Take in their orphans,

811
00:43:06,320 --> 00:43:07,800
allow them
to return to their native places,

812
00:43:07,800 --> 00:43:09,710
and send them to the Imperial Academy
for education.

813
00:43:09,710 --> 00:43:10,400
Also,

814
00:43:10,840 --> 00:43:12,960
Xiao Yao shall be stripped
of all official titles

815
00:43:12,960 --> 00:43:16,890
and banished to Lingnan to address
the flooding along the grain canal.

816
00:43:18,150 --> 00:43:19,920
I will do my utmost

817
00:43:20,190 --> 00:43:21,230
for Ye

818
00:43:21,510 --> 00:43:22,630
until my dying day.

819
00:43:33,210 --> 00:43:35,960
My wish is fulfilled.

820
00:43:37,460 --> 00:43:38,270
I...

821
00:43:39,870 --> 00:43:41,400
am willing to plead guilty.

822
00:43:44,860 --> 00:43:47,190
Then there will be no further punishment.

823
00:43:47,630 --> 00:43:49,950
I hope you will retire
and return to your hometown,

824
00:43:49,950 --> 00:43:51,150
reopen your academy,

825
00:43:51,360 --> 00:43:52,970
devote yourself to scholarship,

826
00:43:52,970 --> 00:43:55,700
and no longer
get involved in political affairs.

827
00:43:58,280 --> 00:44:00,760
I accept the decree.

828
00:44:04,240 --> 00:44:06,630
Liu Zhaolin and the scholars
from Lane 3 of Shanghe Ward

829
00:44:06,630 --> 00:44:08,200
forged handwriting and account books

830
00:44:08,200 --> 00:44:10,200
to frame Prince Jing'an's Mansion.

831
00:44:10,630 --> 00:44:13,190
Considering that this arose from
the divide between nobles and commoners,

832
00:44:13,190 --> 00:44:14,480
and that they have acknowledged
their wrongdoing,

833
00:44:14,480 --> 00:44:15,680
I shall show leniency

834
00:44:16,000 --> 00:44:17,530
and banish them 800 li away.

835
00:44:17,740 --> 00:44:18,870
I accept the decree.

836
00:44:23,770 --> 00:44:26,150
Your Highness, the divide between
nobles and commoners

837
00:44:26,150 --> 00:44:27,280
has long plagued Ye.

838
00:44:27,530 --> 00:44:29,260
Please eradicate it at its root

839
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:32,190
and establish the spring examination
as a permanent system

840
00:44:32,190 --> 00:44:33,320
to ensure fairness.

841
00:44:37,230 --> 00:44:37,880
Granted.

